title: Grateful Dead Live at Capitol Theatre on 1978-11-24
description:
Set 1

Soundcheck: Stagger Lee; I Need A Miracle > Good Lovin'

Set 2

Jack Straw; Sugaree; Me And My Uncle > Big River; Stagger Lee; Passenger; Candyman; New Minglewood Blues; From The Heart Of Me; Loser; The Promised Land

Set 3

I Need A Miracle > Good Lovin'; Friend Of The Devil; Estimated Prophet > Shakedown Street > Drums > Ollin Arrageed (1) > Fire On The Mountain > Sugar Magnolia

Encore: Johnny B. Goode

Jerry Garcia - Guitar
Bob Weir - Guitar
Keith Godchaux - Piano
Phil Lesh - Bass
Bill Kreutzmann - Drums
Mickey Hart - Drums, Hand Drum (1)
Donna Godchaux - Vocals
Hamza El Din - Vocals, Hand Drum (1)
